<p><strong>Step 2: Precision Concrete Cutting and Removal</strong></p>

<strong>Cutting Process:</strong>
<ul><li><strong>Diamond blade wet cutting</strong>: Minimizes dust and provides clean edges</li>
<li><strong>12-18 inch strip width</strong>: Optimal access while minimizing floor disruption</li>
<li><strong>Depth control</strong>: Cut to exact depth avoiding utility damage</li>
